org.apache.flex.compiler.common

Interface IMetaInfo

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IAccessibilityTagNode, IDefaultPropertyTagNode, IEffectTagNode, IEventTagNode, IEventTriggerTagNode, IInspectableTagNode, IMetaTag, IMetaTagNode, IMultiValueMetaTagNode, IResourceBundleTagNode, IStyleTagNode, ITypedTagNode
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AccessibilityTagNode, AlternativeTagNode, BaseDefinitionMetaTagNode, BasicMetaTagNode, DefaultPropertyTagNode, EffectTagNode, EventTagNode, EventTriggerTagNode, InspectableTagNode, MetaTag, MetaTagNode, MultiValueMetaTagNode, ResourceBundleMetaTag, ResourceBundleTagNode, SkinClassTagNode, StyleTagNode, TypedTagNode

    public interface IMetaInfo
    This interface represents the information content of one metadata annotation and is shared by IMetaTagNode and IMetaTag.
